{"TopicId":175695,"ForumId":70,"TopicTitle":"Station that moves in all directions","CreatedByName":"Julien_kerman","CreatedById":180855,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T00:26:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Julien_kerman","CreatedById":180855,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T00:26:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello. Not so long ago, I started to assemble a space station into orbit. But when there is a small \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E push, the station starts to whirl around in all directions.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThank you for helping me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T01:30:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically - \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E on a space station is a bad plan.\u00A0 It\u0027s nearly impossible to have the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E jets positioned perfectly around the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECoM\u003C/abbr\u003E, and then the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E starts to fight the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E, the oscillations begin, and boom.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust use reaction wheels for positioning space stations, and don\u0027t overdo it either.\u00A0 Slow and steady.\u00A0 If you have a really big station, it\u0027s probably better to maneuver the docking ship around the station than to bother moving the station.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E usage is really best for docking procedures and small orbital corrections.\u00A0 I stopped using it for rotation long ago, even for docking.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Julien_kerman","CreatedById":180855,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T16:36:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#212121;font-size:0px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cpre dir=\u0022ltr\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;border:none;color:#212121;font-size:16px;padding:0px .14em 0px 0px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003EOkay, so I do not have to use a RCS but a giroscope to guide it?\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cpre lang=\u0022en\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;border:none;color:#212121;font-size:16px;padding:0px .14em 0px 0px;\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\nSorry for Google Translate\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-06-07T16:41:38Z\u0022 title=\u002206/07/2018 04:41  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJune 7, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Julien_kerman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T19:43:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223394906\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022175695\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528389382\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022180855\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Julien_kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Julien_kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#212121;font-size:0px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cpre dir=\u0022ltr\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;border:none;color:#212121;font-size:16px;padding:0px .14em 0px 0px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\n\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003EOkay, so I do not have to use a RCS but a giroscope to guide it?\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cpre lang=\u0022en\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;border:none;color:#212121;font-size:16px;padding:0px .14em 0px 0px;\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\nSorry for Google Translate\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, use\u00A0the reaction wheel parts. Make sure they are equally distanced from the station\u2019s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECOM\u003C/abbr\u003E. If they\u2019re unbalanced, that can lead to stability issues.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Julien_kerman","CreatedById":180855,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T20:42:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223395042\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022175695\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221528400587\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, use\u00A0the reaction wheel parts. Make sure they are equally distanced from the station\u2019s \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECOM\u003C/abbr\u003E. If they\u2019re unbalanced, that can lead to stability issues.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#212121;font-size:0px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cpre dir=\u0022ltr\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;border:none;color:#212121;font-size:29px;padding:0px .14em 0px 0px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003EOk I will try\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cpre lang=\u0022en\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;border:none;color:#212121;font-size:29px;padding:0px .14em 0px 0px;\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\n\n\u00A0\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Julien_kerman","CreatedById":180855,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-08T00:06:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#212121;font-size:0px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cpre dir=\u0022ltr\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;border:none;color:#212121;font-size:29px;padding:0px .14em 0px 0px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan lang=\u0022en\u0022 xml:lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003EPerfect! it works! Thank you very much for your help!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"}]}